title: Ginza no Banneko
sinopse:
After both separately being invited by a guy owning a bar to manage it, popular cabaret girl Suzu Miyake and genius bartender Shouko Amemiya arrive at the bar a few days before it's reopening... and realize that they've been tricked. However, since they each have nowhere to go, they commit to managing the bar together, but...

(Source: Media Do International/Beaglee)
